# Automated Monitoring & Self-Healing System

## Overview
Implements monitoring, alerting, and self-healing for cloud applications using Prometheus, Grafana, Terraform, and automation scripts. Demonstrates operational excellence and SRE-level automation.

## Tech Stack
- Monitoring: Prometheus, Grafana
- Cloud: AWS CloudWatch / GCP Monitoring
- Automation: Python / Bash
- Terraform (IaC)
- Alerts: Slack / Email notifications

## Features
- Real-time monitoring dashboards
- Alerts for application downtime
- Automated self-healing scripts
- Infrastructure provisioning via Terraform

## Architecture Diagram
![Architecture Diagram](./docs/architecture.png)

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repo
2. Setup monitoring stack using Terraform:
   ```bash
   cd infra
   terraform init
   terraform apply
